<title>H. Leslie Adams, Composer & Pianist</title>
<meta name="keywords" content="African American Composer, African American Pianist, African American Professor, Love Rejoices, Twelve Etudes">
<meta name="description" content="A brief profile of H. Leslie Adams, an African American composer, pianist and professor who was born in Cleveland, Ohio in 1932.  Some recent CDs are listed, along with the performers and catalog numbers.  A link is  also provided to the composer's own Web site.">
