				<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in;" align="left">
				<span style>Turner, Diana.&nbsp; Leslie Adams, composer in <i style>
				Call and post</i> [Cleveland] v6n6 (1983/X/17).</span></p>
				<p class="MsoList" style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt 0.25in;" align="left">
				<span style="font-size: 12pt;">White, Evelyn Davidson.<span style>&nbsp;
				</span><i>Choral music by Afro-American composers; A selected, 
				annotated bibliography</i>.<span style>&nbsp; </span>2<sup>nd</sup> 
				ed.<span style>&nbsp; </span>Metuchen: Scarecrow Press, 1996.<span style>&nbsp;
