				<i style><span style>Who's who in entertainment.&nbsp; </span></i>
				<span style>Wilmette IL:&nbsp; Macmillan Directory Division, 1990.</span></p>
				<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin: 0in 0in 0pt 0.25in; text-indent: -0.25in;" align="left">
				<span style>Williams, Yvonne C.&nbsp; Leslie Adams and the making of 
				the opera <i style>Blake; </i>An interview with the composer in<i style> 
				New perspectives on music; Esssays in honor of Eileen Southern</i>, 
